Name: Clear-IISCentralCertProvider
Synopsis: Removes configuration information from the IIS central certificate store.

Name: Clear-IISConfigCollection
Synopsis: Clears an IIS configuration collection.

Name: Disable-IISCentralCertProvider
Synopsis: Disables the IIS central certificate store.

Name: Disable-IISSharedConfig
Synopsis: Disables IIS shared configuration.

Name: Enable-IISCentralCertProvider
Synopsis: Enables the IIS central certificate store.

Name: Enable-IISSharedConfig
Synopsis: Enables shared configuration.

Name: Export-IISConfiguration
Synopsis: Exports the IIS configuration and machine keys.

Name: Get-IISAppPool
Synopsis: Gets configuration information for an IIS Application Pool.

Name: Get-IISCentralCertProvider
Synopsis: Gets information about the IIS central certificate store.

Name: Get-IISConfigAttributeValue
Synopsis: Gets a configuration attribute value from an IIS configuration section or configuration element attribute.

Name: Get-IISConfigCollection
Synopsis: Gets a configuration collection object from an IIS configuration section or a configuration element.

Name: Get-IISConfigCollectionElement
Synopsis: Gets a configuration element object from an IIS configuration collection.

Name: Get-IISConfigElement
Synopsis: Gets a configuration element object from an IIS configuration section or a configuration element.

Name: Get-IISConfigSection
Synopsis: Gets a configuration section object to work further with the IIS Configuration Store.

Name: Get-IISServerManager
Synopsis: Gets the IISAdministration view of IIS ServerManager.

Name: Get-IISSharedConfig
Synopsis: Gets IIS shared configuration status.

Name: Get-IISSite
Synopsis: Gets configuration information for an IIS Web site.

Name: Get-IISSiteBinding
Synopsis: Get-IISSiteBinding [-Name] <string> [[-BindingInformation] <string>] [[-Protocol] <string>] [<CommonParameters>]

Name: New-IISConfigCollectionElement
Synopsis: Creates a new configuration element object in an IIS configuration collection.

Name: New-IISSite
Synopsis: Creates an IIS Web site.

Name: New-IISSiteBinding
Synopsis: New-IISSiteBinding [-Name] <string> [-BindingInformation] <string> [[-Protocol] <string>] [[-CertificateThumbPrint] <string>] [[-SslFlag] <SslFlags>] [[-CertStoreLocation] <string>] [-Force] [-Passthru] [<CommonParameters>]

Name: Remove-IISConfigAttribute
Synopsis: Removes a configuration attribute from an IIS configuration section or configuration element attribute.

Name: Remove-IISConfigCollectionElement
Synopsis: Removes a configuration element object from an IIS configuration collection.

Name: Remove-IISConfigElement
Synopsis: Removes a specified configuration element.

Name: Remove-IISSite
Synopsis: Removes a web site from an IIS server.

Name: Remove-IISSiteBinding
Synopsis: Remove-IISSiteBinding [-Name] <string> [-BindingInformation] <string> [[-Protocol] <string>] [-RemoveConfigOnly] [-WhatIf] [-Confirm] [<CommonParameters>]

Name: Reset-IISServerManager
Synopsis: Resets the IISAdministration view of the IIS ServerManager.

Name: Set-IISCentralCertProvider
Synopsis: Sets property values for the IIS central certificate store.

Name: Set-IISCentralCertProviderCredential
Synopsis: Modifies the user account credentials for the IIS certificate store.

Name: Set-IISConfigAttributeValue
Synopsis: Sets a configuration attribute value for an IIS configuration section or configuration element attribute.

Name: Start-IISCommitDelay
Synopsis: Instructs the IIS configuration system to delay the commitment of changes.

Name: Start-IISSite
Synopsis: Starts an existing site on the IIS server.

Name: Stop-IISCommitDelay
Synopsis: Instructs the IIS configuration system to resume the commitment of changes.

Name: Stop-IISSite
Synopsis: Stops an IIS Web site.
